cff-version: 1.2.0
title: >-
  Chlef-Biostat-2026: a trilingual web platform for
  a cross-sectional study on adolescent overweight in
  the Wilaya of Chlef, Algeria
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite it using the
  metadata from this file.
