    affiliation: >-
      Faculty of Medicine, Hassiba Benbouali University
      of Chlef (UHBC), Algeria
repository-code: 'https://github.com/Touil-Elhadj/chlef-touilelhadj'
url: 'https://github.com/Touil-Elhadj/chlef-touilelhadj'
abstract: >-
  Chlef-Biostat-2026 is a self-contained trilingual
  (Arabic / French / English, RTL-aware) data-collection
  web platform for a cross-sectional study on adolescent
  overweight in the Wilaya of Chlef, Algeria (n = 1220,
  ages 14-19, academic year 2025-2026). The analytic
  engine is provided by the separately-distributed
  biostat-php Composer library (touilelhadj/biostat-php),
  which implements descriptive, bivariate and multivariate
  statistical methods (logistic regression, GLMM by PQL,
  GEE, MICE with Rubin's pooling, VIF, Box-Tidwell,
  Benjamini-Hochberg FDR) in pure PHP without dependency
  on R or SPSS.
